<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV104">
<l>kaṭuṅkavantaṉ vakkaraṉka raṉmuraṉci rammavai</l>
<l>yiṭantukūṟu ceytapalpa ṭaittaṭakkai māyaṉē</l>
<l>kiṭantiruntu niṉṟiyaṅku pōtuniṉṉa poṟkaḻaṟ</l>
<l>ṟoṭarntuvīḷvi lātatōrto ṭarccinalka vēṇṭumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Wonderful Lord with broad arms with many weapons that dislodged and smashed</l>
<l>The heads of the harsh Kabandha, [Dantā]vakra, Khara, [and] Mura!</l>
<l>Do grant a continuous, uninterrupted chain [of thought]</l>
<l>of Your golden feet even when lying, sitting, standing, and walking about!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
